{"tid":133731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 曾俊華今早交提名　將成首個報名參選人","createTime":"2017-02-25T01:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T05:49:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f513c2bfbb5db75ead5be555ceb56d80d42cb5a6","tid":133731,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:01:54.000Z","msg":"特首選舉下周三(3月1日)截止提名，參選人曾俊華預計今早10時半到灣仔選舉事務處遞交報名表，將成為首位報名參選人士。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華競選辦今早突然發出通知，指曾俊華將於稍後時間到選舉管理委員會，遞交行政長官選舉提名表格予選舉主任。競選辦指，已有足夠提名入閘。<br />\n<br />\n手握最多提名票的另一參選人林鄭月娥預料下周一(27日)公布政綱後，周二(28日)提交報名表。"},{"pid":"4f7cd2a8a266e810629af91abac397f2f35a3d7a","tid":133731,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170225/s00001/1487983979870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170225%2Fs00001%2F1487983979870&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTeci7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=75e8f07d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170225%2Fs00001%2F1487983979870&h=7288289b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170225/s00001/1487983979870</a>"},{"pid":"a0b274c6396b137a7959ce555eb3e6a7a292567e","tid":133731,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2debabf3488ce14abb68c85be27b6b107a334ae9","tid":133731,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"梗係要快啦，一陣驚人彈弓手<br />\n<br />\n但我有得投票咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66268d8fbf660e9e31166198e7a2b10745ec5017","tid":133731,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T01:04:33.000Z","msg":"防提名轉軚"},{"pid":"6f9cee37a39a301fddbbf6